Interface DistRotatingMachine

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusRef<DistBus>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DistBusAdapter, DistNonContribBus, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DistGeneratorImpl, DistIndMotorImpl, DistMixedLoadImpl, DistMotorImpl, DistRotatingMachineImpl, DistSynMotorImpl

    public interface DistRotatingMachine
extends DistNonContribBus
    A representation of the model object 'Rotating Machine Adapter'. Adapter for rotating machine, including generator, indMotor, synMotor and mixedLoad.
    See Also:
    DistAdapterPackage.getDistRotatingMachine()
